Dynamic table display template for SemanticSchemas categories.

Parameters:
* category - The category name (without namespace prefix)
* properties - Comma-separated list of property page names

Renders a wikitable with one row per property (hidden when empty) and
reverse relationship rows discovered dynamically from the SMW store.
Uses #arraymap with \n delimiter which skips empty results (no blank rows).
